OL,3,CThree football fans banned from
OL,4,Cmatches after Muratti Vase disorder
OL,6,FThree people from Guernsey have been
OL,7,Fbanned from attending football matches
OL,8,Forganised by Jersey and Guernsey's
OL,9,FFootball Associations (FA) for
OL,10,Ffighting and setting off flares during
OL,11,Fthe men's Muratti Vase final last
OL,12,Fmonth.
OL,14,FOfficials from the authorities say
OL,15,Fthey were "appalled at the disgraceful
OL,16,Fbehaviour shown by a minority" of fans
OL,17,Fduring the game at Springfield Stadium
OL,18,Fon 16 May.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
