FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781684278
OL,3,CThree football fans banned from
OL,4,Cmatches after Muratti Vase disorder
OL,6,FSeparately, the States of Jersey
OL,7,FPolice say they have now completed an
OL,8,Finvestigation into the disorder and
OL,9,Fthat criminal proceedings may be
OL,10,Fopened.
OL,12,FThe force say behaviour, including
OL,13,Fentering the field of play, throwing
OL,14,Fobjects and engaging in threatening or
OL,15,Fabusive conduct, "have no place in
OL,16,Ffootball or the wider community and
OL,17,Fwill not be tolerated".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781684278
OL,3,CThree football fans banned from
OL,4,Cmatches after Muratti Vase disorder
OL,6,FIn a statement, Tim Pryor, CEO of the
OL,7,FJersey FA, said: "This sends out a
OL,8,Fclear and strong message that this
OL,9,Fkind of behaviour will not be
OL,10,Ftolerated at local football matches.
OL,12,F"The huge majority of the 1,500 people
OL,13,Fin attendance at the men's Muratti
OL,14,FVase final behaved well, enjoyed the
OL,15,Foccasion and supported their team in
OL,16,Fthe right way.
OL,18,F"A small minority crossed the line,
OL,19,Fand they will not be welcome back at
OL,20,FSpringfield for future Jersey FA
OL,21,Frepresentative team matches.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781684278
OL,3,CThree football fans banned from
OL,4,Cmatches after Muratti Vase disorder
OL,6,F"Our thanks to the authorities for
OL,7,Ftheir work on identifying those
OL,8,Finvolved."
OL,10,FGary Roberts, the Guernsey FA's Chief
OL,11,FExecutive, added that he was "appalled
OL,12,Fat the disgraceful behaviour"
OL,13,Fdemonstrated by those involved in the
OL,14,Fdisorder.
OL,16,FMr Roberts said: "The behaviour
OL,17,Fwitnessed that day has no place at
OL,18,Fthese matches.
OL,26,@pD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781684278
OL,3,CThree football fans banned from
OL,4,Cmatches after Muratti Vase disorder
OL,6,F"This announcement makes it abundantly
OL,7,Fclear that behaviour of this nature
OL,8,Fwill not be tolerated and has defined
OL,9,Fconsequences.
OL,11,F"Those identified as being involved in
OL,12,Fthe incidents at the Muratti Final
OL,13,Fwill not be able to attend future
OL,14,FGuernsey FA Representative matches at
OL,15,FVictoria Park, which is a strong
OL,16,Fmessage we hope will be appreciated by
OL,17,Fgenuine football spectators and the
OL,18,Fwider community."
OL,26,@zD@QO]
